2.quote: Mm! The fortune slip was right...

3.name: Thoma
3.quote: Hey! What was that for?

0.name: Tighnari
0.quote: Don't be afraid to make mistakes. It's all part of the learning process.

1.name: Tighnari
1.quote: The value of knowledge cannot simply be quantified in monetary terms.

2.name: Tighnari
2.quote: Let's nip that in the bud!

3.name: Tighnari
3.quote: Why is there a chest here?

0.name: Venti
0.quote: Sure, I'll play you another tune, but it'll cost you an apple.

1.name: Venti
1.quote: Let's go jumping in puddles and see who can make the biggest splash!

2.name: Venti
2.quote: Think you can get away?

3.name: Venti
3.quote: *clears throat* Have you heard The Ballad of the Treasure Chest?

0.name: Wanderer
0.quote: You're so happy just to see the sun again? How childish.

1.name: Wanderer
1.quote: A simple breeze like this... Even you can conjure it, right?

2.name: Wanderer
2.quote: You dare to gaze upon me!?

3.name: Wanderer
3.quote: Hah, you even want this?

0.name: Wriothesley
0.quote: Hmm... This is a different kind of cold than what I'm used to.

1.name: Wriothesley
1.quote: Morning. What do the papers have to say about today's weather forecast?

2.name: Wriothesley
2.quote: This could get a little chilly.

3.name: Wriothesley
3.quote: Stay cool and face your guilt!

0.name: Xiangling
0.quote: Is there time for a quick snack? I'll whip one up in no time!

1.name: Xiangling
1.quote: If there's nothing better to do, we could go foraging for ingredients...

2.name: Xiangling
2.quote: Out of the frying pan, into the fire!

3.name: Xiangling
3.quote: Now I've got stomach cramps...

0.name: Xianyun
0.quote: Ugh, what a dreadful racket...

1.name: Xianyun
1.quote: Hmm? Spare me that look, is it not your turn to prepare luncheon today?

2.name: Xianyun
2.quote: Make way for the adeptus!

3.name: Xianyun
3.quote: These could be salvaged for parts.

0.name: Xiao
0.quote: Reduced to just standing around. How absurd.

1.name: Xiao
1.quote: The damned will sooner die again than lay a hand on me.

2.name: Xiao
2.quote: If it's useful, I'll take it.

3.name: Xiao
3.quote: Why would anyone want... *sigh* Forget it, it's not my concern.

0.name: Xilonen
0.quote: Perfect weather for a nap in the workshop...

1.name: Xilonen
1.quote: Achoo! ...Ah, I'm awake now.

2.name: Xilonen
2.quote: Hear the echoes of the valley!

3.name: Xilonen
3.quote: Let the mountain's veins boil!

0.name: Xingqiu
0.quote: 'Twas on a deserted moonlit night that the hero approached the vile dragon's limpid lair...

1.name: Xingqiu
1.quote: I never embark on a journey without a good book to accompany me.

2.name: Xingqiu
2.quote: Witness the power of Guhua!

3.name: Xingqiu
3.quote: Let me weave you a verse.

0.name: Xinyan
0.quote: I just came up with an awesome new riff, wanna hear it?

1.name: Xinyan
1.quote: Whatever's going on over there... Looks pretty rock 'n' roll to me!

2.name: Xinyan
2.quote: Time to celebrate! Ready? 1, 2, 3, 4...

3.name: Xinyan
3.quote: Woohoo! Let me hear ya!

0.name: Yae Miko
0.quote: If this rain keeps up, my fur will be dripping wet...

1.name: Yae Miko
1.quote: Many people dread the sound of thunder... To me, it sounds fondly familiar.

2.name: Yae Miko
2.quote: Well, what do we have here?

3.name: Yae Miko
3.quote: Don't tell me that's everything...

0.name: Yanfei
0.quote: I'll remind you again: The law can be both a help and a hindrance.

1.name: Yanfei
1.quote: The case before us... is a strange and unprecedented one indeed.

2.name: Yanfei
2.quote: Ooh, we can definitely write this off as "incidental gains."

3.name: Yanfei
3.quote: Huh, let's appraise the value on this...

0.name: Yaoyao
0.quote: Ooh, what's happening over there? Can we take a sneaky peek, huh? Can we?

1.name: Yaoyao
1.quote: The weather's so nice. Let's go have a walk around the harbor!

2.name: Yaoyao
2.quote: Pack everything up nice and carefully. Don't drop anything!

3.name: Yaoyao
3.quote: Wooow! These'll last us for days!

0.name: Yelan
0.quote: I got a new letter from an informant. Looks like the situation has changed again.

1.name: Yelan
1.quote: It's getting a little cold... Time to bundle up.

2.name: Yelan
2.quote: Things are about to get dicey.

3.name: Yelan
3.quote: Treasure... one way to draw your target out of hiding.

0.name: Yoimiya
0.quote: Fireworks are for now, but friends are forever.

1.name: Yoimiya
1.quote: If we've got nothing else to do, why don't I tell you a story?

2.name: Yoimiya
2.quote: Time for a light show!

3.name: Yoimiya
3.quote: Ooh! Will we find any firework materials in here?

0.name: Yumemizuki Mizuki
0.quote: That dream last night tasted wonderful. Thank you for sharing it with me.

1.name: Yumemizuki Mizuki
1.quote: Still need to go through last quarter's financial report... What a headache.

2.name: Yumemizuki Mizuki
2.quote: Cast your worries to the wind.

3.name: Yumemizuki Mizuki
3.quote: Ah, what a nice find!

0.name: Yun Jin
0.quote: *gasp* D—Did you hear that? Whew, it really startled me.

1.name: Yun Jin
1.quote: (Translated) Fie! This cold shall be mine end!

2.name: Yun Jin
2.quote: The troupe appreciates any donation.

3.name: Yun Jin
3.quote: Hmm... Anything the troupe could use on our journey?

0.name: Zhongli
0.quote: Every journey has its final day. Don't rush.

1.name: Zhongli
1.quote: I hope today too shall be prosperous.

2.name: Zhongli
2.quote: One man's stone is another man's gem...

3.name: Zhongli
3.quote: Unsolicited... and all the more valuable for it.
